Burning Man 2023, before it turned into a mud show. Thankful for the experience and people that were there for me. It was challenging. Had some beautiful moments this year, too. Birthday cake in the middle of apocalypse melted my heart 🫶 Emotions might change later, but as of right now, I think I’ll make a long pause before coming back to Black Rock City.

Loved being a part of the new @greenday music video. I remember when I was a rebellious teenager, loved this band so much and thought I’ll never listen to any other music, but rock 😁 Time changes you. But teenage dreams do come true sometimes. Meanwhile, the american dream is actually killing me. 🖤
My favorite part is to tell people my name while I’m there
Snowboarding after a decade – all bones intact 😅
Jumping on the recap trend last minute. Seems like 2023 had some really good moments. 🎆
